#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/docs/guides/cms/dokuwiki_server.md:26
#, no-wrap
msgid "Documentation can take many forms in an organization. Having a repository that you can reference for that documentation is invaluable. A wiki (which means _quick_ in Hawaiian), is a way to keep documentation, process notes, corporate knowledge bases, and even code examples, in a centralized location. IT professionals who maintain a wiki, even secretly, have a built-in insurance policy against forgetting an obscure routine.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/docs/guides/cms/dokuwiki_server.md:28
#, no-wrap
msgid "DokuWiki is a mature, fast, wiki that runs without a database, has built in security features, and is relatively easy to deploy. For more information on what DokuWiki can do, check out their [web page](https://www.dokuwiki.org/dokuwiki).\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/docs/guides/cms/dokuwiki_server.md:30
#, no-wrap
msgid "DokuWiki is just one of many wikis available, though it's a pretty good one. One big pro is that DokuWiki is relatively lightweight and can run on a server that is already running other services, provided you have space and memory available.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Title ##
#: ../src/docs/guides/cms/dokuwiki_server.md:31
#, no-wrap
msgid "Installing Dependencies"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/docs/guides/cms/dokuwiki_server.md:34
#, no-wrap
msgid "The minimum PHP version for DokuWiki is now 7.2, which is exactly what Rocky Linux 8 comes with. Rocky Linux 9.0 comes with PHP version 8.0, which is also fully supported. We are specifying packages here that may already be installed:\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/docs/guides/cms/dokuwiki_server.md:36
#, no-wrap
msgid "`dnf install tar wget httpd php php-gd php-xml php-json php-mbstring`\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/docs/guides/cms/dokuwiki_server.md:38
#, no-wrap
msgid "You will see a list of additional dependencies that will be installed and this prompt:\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/docs/guides/cms/dokuwiki_server.md:40
#, no-wrap
msgid "`Is this ok [y/N]:`\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/docs/guides/cms/dokuwiki_server.md:42
#, no-wrap
msgid "Go ahead and answer with \"y\" and hit 'Enter' to install.\n"
msgstr ""

