#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/docs/guides/cms/dokuwiki_server.md:105
#, no-wrap
msgid "Now that we have our environment ready to go, let's  get the latest stable version of DokuWiki. You can find this by going to [the download page](https://download.dokuwiki.org/) and on the left-hand side of the page under \"Version\" you will see \"Stable (Recommended) (direct link).\"\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/docs/guides/cms/dokuwiki_server.md:107
#, no-wrap
msgid "Right-click on the \"(direct link)\" portion of this and copy the link address. In the console of your DokuWiki server, type \"wget\" and a space and then paste in your copied link in the terminal. You should get something like this:\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/docs/guides/cms/dokuwiki_server.md:109
